## Performance Guidelines

- Use `dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })` for heavy client components (editor, publish panel)
- Limit Framer Motion animations on long lists — only animate newly loaded items (see `PostList.js` `prevCountRef` pattern)
- Use `dedupingInterval` in SWR to prevent duplicate API calls
- Avoid `will-change` on many elements
- Use `React.memo()` only when profiling shows unnecessary re-renders — don't prememo everything
- When extracting sub-components that receive callbacks as props, wrap callbacks in `useCallback` in the parent

---

## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

1. **Do NOT copy-paste `useSWRInfinite` boilerplate** — always use `useInfiniteList` or `useInfiniteCursor`
2. **Do NOT hand-roll error/empty/skeleton states** — use `ErrorState`, `EmptyState`, `PostItemSkeleton`, `PostSkeleton`
3. **Do NOT hand-roll buttons with inline styles** — use `<Button variant="...">` from `UI/`
4. **Do NOT hand-roll avatar circles** — use `<Avatar>` from `UI/`
5. **Do NOT hand-roll inline spinners** — `Button` has built-in `loading` prop; use `<Spinner>` for standalone cases
6. **Do NOT hand-roll click-outside listeners** — use `useOutsideClick` hook
7. **Do NOT hand-roll `body.style.overflow = 'hidden'` in modals** — use `useBodyScrollLock` hook
8. **Do NOT hand-roll scroll listeners for sticky nav** — use `useScrollEffect` hook
9. **Do NOT hand-roll `input[type=file]` + upload logic** — use `useFileUpload` hook
10. **Do NOT use named imports for axios instances** — they are default exports
11. **Do NOT hardcode Vietnamese/English strings in JSX** — use `next-intl` translations
12. **Do NOT create duplicate service functions** for the same endpoint
13. **Do NOT duplicate extension lists** — use `tiptapBaseExtensions.js` factory
14. **Do NOT use `findIndex` for deduplication** — use `Set` for O(n) performance
15. **Do NOT create 900-line utility files** — split into focused modules under a directory
16. **Do NOT store functions in React state** without wrapping: `setState(() => fn)` not `setState(fn)`
17. **Do NOT mix 3 styling approaches in one component** — be consistent
18. **Do NOT import `Post/PostSkeleton`** — file no longer exists. Use `Post/PostItemSkeleton` or `Shared/PostSkeleton`
19. **Do NOT import `PublishPanel` from `Category/`** — canonical location is `Editor/PublishPanel`
20. **Do NOT duplicate `MasonryPostGrid + ErrorState` inline** — use `PostFeed` component

