## Auth & Roles

- Two roles: `USER_ROLES.USER` ('user'), `USER_ROLES.ADMIN` ('admin')
- Auth token stored in `localStorage` as `'token'`
- `axiosPrivateInstance` reads token from localStorage and sets `Authorization: Bearer {token}`
- Permission checks: `isAdmin(role)`, `canWritePosts(role)`, `isSuperAdmin()` (from authService, checks JWT)
- Protected pages check auth in `useEffect` and redirect or show login modal

